Package org.forgerock.openidm.sync.impl

Class ReconQueryResult

java.lang.Object
org.forgerock.openidm.sync.impl.ReconQueryResult
public class ReconQueryResult extends Object
Contains an iterator over the recon query results as well as a paging cookie relating to the query.
